Marianna Hill https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marianna_Hill 0 Marianna Hill (born February 9, 1942), sometimes credited as Mariana Hill, is an American actress who has predominantly worked in American television and is known for her starring role in the feature western film High Plains Drifter (1973) as well as many roles on television series in the 1960s and 1970s.
